Statgrab
========

Building and installing
-----------------------

    ruby extconf.rb
    make
    su
    make install

Sample program
--------------

    require 'statgrab'
    sg = Statgrab.new
    puts "CPU Usage: %.1f%%" % sg.cpu_percents[:user]

